EN: Reading is the ladder of human progress.

ZH: 家长应该鼓励孩子多阅读。
EN: Parents should encourage children to read more.

ZH: 小说是我最喜欢的阅读材料。
EN: Novels are my favorite reading material.

ZH: 阅读可以带给我们乐趣和启发。
EN: Reading can bring us joy and inspiration.

ZH: 我们应该养成每天阅读的习惯。
EN: We should develop a habit of reading every day.

ZH: 这个周末我要安静地享受阅读的乐趣。
EN: I will quietly enjoy the pleasure of reading this weekend.

ZH: 我们每天都在不断地学习阅读新事物。
EN: We are constantly learning to read new things every day.

ZH: 阅读让我感到平静而充实。
